  description: "Attacks a single enemy, increasing the Control-Free Rate by 25% and
    Armor by 30% for 2 turns. Also restores HP to the ally behind the caster equal
    to 100% of the caster\u2019s Damage. If there is no ally behind the caster or
    the ally is dead, the healing is applied to the caster instead."
